302
00:16:20,100 --> 00:16:20,670
Yes, Your Majesty.

303
00:16:24,590 --> 00:16:25,730
Father.

304
00:16:29,310 --> 00:16:30,130
Mingxuan,

305
00:16:30,270 --> 00:16:31,580
