327
00:17:28,420 --> 00:17:28,980
Yes, Father.

328
00:17:36,110 --> 00:17:36,590
Father.

329
00:17:38,380 --> 00:17:39,530
My dear daughter,

330
00:17:39,760 --> 00:17:41,210
the weather is so nice today.

331
00:17:41,240 --> 00:17:42,400
